**Overall:** The idea needs to significantly strengthen its conceptual foundation, rigorously commit to all aspects of the data description (especially UV stability), and provide a more convincing roadmap for demonstrating general quantum stability beyond highly simplified cases. If the UV stability aspect cannot be rigorously addressed, the idea fundamentally fails to meet the prompt's requirements and a new idea should be considered.
